replies.body:
Mana pots.... y? just y? WHY DO YOU HATE MAGES SO HARD? Why can only manaless harass bs champs have infinite sustain now with healing crits while mages can barely scrape together a combo? It's like Mages are stuck with the dollar menu while everyone else gets the damn combo meal. I don't even want to get into how badly the lack of sustain is hurting supports with beefed up adcs.
 {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}

on the other hand my favourite item has returned {{item:3123}} with a fancy new upgrade {{item:3033}} 
I missed this item so bad. It really leveled the playing field against retarded sustained assassins.
